<body><div class=WordSection1>
<div class="brand">📚 ENGLISH CODING · 영어코딩</div>
<h1>🧊 M003 Extension — Coordinate Pixel Art</h1>
<p><strong>Topic:</strong> Reading (x, y) · <strong>Course:</strong> 3D Coordinates · <strong>Level:</strong> Extension · <strong>Time:</strong> about 20 minutes</p>
<p>No computer — just a pencil. Count <strong>x</strong> left → right, <strong>y</strong> bottom → up. Every square has an address <strong>(x, y)</strong> — read it, colour the square.</p>
<hr />
<h2>1 · Predict 🔮</h2>
<p>Colour every square in the list. What picture appears?</p>
<pre><code>(4,1) (4,2) (4,3) (4,4)
(2,5) (3,5) (4,5) (5,5) (6,5)
(3,6) (4,6) (5,6)
(4,7)
</code></pre>
